Package: rcvr
Type: Package
Title: Read and Identify Cast-Vote-Record Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yuki", "Atsusaka", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "yuki.atsusaka@example.com")
Description: Reads cast-vote-record (CVR) CSV files from ranked-choice voting
    elections and prepends a standardized election identifier derived from the
    file name. Identifier metadata is linked to the archive of American RCV
    elections at <https://www.archive-rcv.com>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
